                <span class="text-white font-medium  group-hover:text-black">Continue with Github</span>
            </a>
<button  class="flex items-center mb-2 justify-center transition ease-in-out delay-50 px-3 py-2.5 space-x-2 bg-gray-800 border border-slate-600 rounded-md hover:bg-gray-100 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-gray-600 focus:ring-opacity-50 group" onclick="handleAn(event)">

